   <narrative xml:lang="EN">200 Children of Sri Lanka receive Free Education</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sunray Foundation intends to supply monthly food rations along with funds to support the educational needs of 200 underprivileged children living in the central province of Sri Lanka. These identified children are living in single parent homes or with relatives or guardians. Unlike the children living in Sri Lanken orphanages. who are well provided for,  these displaced children often suffer from the lack of adequate food, clothing and education. their mental health needs are not been addressed</narrative>
  </description>
